  "texts": [
    "Using this model, a methodology for the valuation of assets was proposed by [57].Financial applications have been covered in works such as [132], where the authors collected data from one hundred female employees working in Coimbatore, India.",
    "Their technique was improved in [186].",
    "Xu et al. [233] were concerned with predicting business failure via the selection of financial ratios.",
    "They use an explicitly designed parameter reduction technique for this purpose.",
    "Their methodology is applied to real datasets from listed firms in China."
  ]
}